raktha tilakam ( telugu : రక్త తిలకం ) is a 1988 tollywood action - family film directed by b. gopal and produced by k.ashok kumar on sri usha art productions banner .   starring venkatesh and amala played the lead roles and music is composed by chakravarthy .   the film was a remake of tamil film thaimel aanai and was also remade in hindi as pratikar in 1991 .   the film was hit at the box office .